  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To test the safety of high dose spinal in elective CS after prolonged sitting position.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective double-blind randomized study, designed to include cases in two groups
      (using epical program for sample size calculation), one study groups and one control group
      (parallel). Each group should have at least 30 female patients scheduled for elective
      caesarean section with a total of 60 cases.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
